  "title": "Contract Data Analyst (FMCG) - Up to 6.5K / WEST #HHL",
  "description": "<p></p><h3><strong>Job Description</strong></h3><ul><li><p>Support supplier onboarding and execution of traceability compliance programs</p></li><li><p>Extract, validate, and analyze data using <strong>SQL, APIs, and ETL workflows</strong></p></li><li><p>Build and maintain dashboards using <strong>Excel, Tableau, and/or Power BI</strong></p></li><li><p>Work closely with platform vendors to ensure data integrity</p></li><li><p>Prepare reports and insights for internal stakeholders</p></li><li><p>Manage deployment timelines, communications, and documentation</p></li><li><p>Coordinate meetings, track actions, and maintain program FAQs</p></li><li><p>Perform validations within traceability platforms as required</p></li></ul><h3><strong>Requirement</strong></h3><ul><li><p>Min Degree in Business Analytics, Computer Science, or related discipline</p></li><li><p>Min <strong>2 years’ experience</strong> in data analysis, BI, or reporting roles</p></li><li><p>Strong hands-on skills in <strong>Excel, SQL, Tableau / Power BI</strong></p></li><li><p>Experience with <strong>ETL, API integration, Power Automate</strong></p></li><li><p>Comfortable working with multiple stakeholders and vendors</p></li><li><p>Detail-oriented with strong analytical and problem-solving skills<br /><br />If interested, please email me at alexgoh@recruitexpress.com.sg or telegram @alexgohhl<br /></p><p>Alex Goh Hock Leong</p><p>(CEI.No: R1763413 l Recruit Express Pte Ltd (Healthcare & Life Science) | 99C4599).</p></li></ul>",
